description: Redevelopment comprising the erection of a 21 storey building to provide a maximum of 201 market and affordable residential flats (and no less than 195 residential flats) (Class C3), retail uses (A1/A2/A3/A4/A5), nursery and community space, provision of basement parking, servicing and ancillary space, highway works, new vehicular and pedestrian access and associated hard and soft landscaping (Building 3).
